Significance of transformation and distribution of energy 
===============================================
It is the single energy exists everywhere in this universe in the form of waves. It is the state of energy within the object that makes/transform the object form one form into another form. It is the state of energy within life also that look like live than the static object. In fact every thing is in state of live only but for looking it you need better state of observation.
Every state of object/energy are in under transformation already, they exists in state of streaming only you are able to observe or not it depends up on the thinning power of your
observation.

Every lives have different power of senses, thinking, realization so on, that is also based on the arrangement /architecture of energy within them. Due to this arrangement one live can realize different than another life.

Ex-
If human look animal some one look for enjoyment,  some one look for killing them, some one look for making pet, some one look for observe their activity so on. These differentiation
only in human being but when any hungry state of lion look Deer their energy perceive towards deer for their food only.
This is due to state of energy withing life who look the things differently. 

transformation and distribution of energy
------------------------------------------------------
