If your thinking work in proper direction then it automatically come one track of single direction that makes your life healing day by day, it perceive towards the transformation of life, it analyse in the direction of within, it plan for transformation, it try to realize/look/observe the transformation, it think the value of transformation in life,it can think what you living the life that is dust of life, it can detect the proper reason of any scenario.

Transformation
--------------------
Each and every human have power of their transformation and only they can transform themselves. You can transform yourself from body/mind to energy/observation. If you really ready/agree then  none can touch your workout, none can know what you are doing except the person who are in your state. Transformation don't need anything except you highly motivated dedication from inside.
You can understand the value of transformation when you are under transformation by your workout. Whatever going inside changes can be easily/lightly detected by your observation.*** 

***Transformation is independent from the arrangement make by human being, you can move as your heart allow is enough to maintain the velocity***

Distribution
-----------------
Distribution is another state of energy when you got sufficient transformation to your self, you may realize you get lost, you may realize it is not you, you may realize it is the energy system within this body who maintain/perceive towards any activity.
At this state there is no GOD, No LIFE, only energy exits everywhere and injected in the object and due to arrangement of energy within object, the object look like life.
At this state you can't keep the energy collected but you should distribute the same energy to another lower sate of energy system. Even you want or not it not depends up on
your wishes it automatically get distributed.

Ex-
If water in the pond get full then it automatically flow form it shore, the flow of water may be done by some arrangement but overall it flow automatically, if you continuous supply energy to your self after long period of time it automatically get distributed.
***Everything follow the principle of energy properly but we are unaware about it***

Distribution of energy need proper language,statement ,speaking,writing,activities. During distribution of energy you take help from information gather by science,physics, chemistry, geography, society, government, rule,right, humanity,honesty..etc.

***Transformation of energy is independent from human made arrangement but distribution of energy need the human made stuff***
